data.description: Spacious home with a fantastic layout on one of the largest lots in the community! Relax in the enclosed sunroom that overlook the oversized .394 acre lot. The yard is perfect for football, gatherings or gardening! Also has large shed for storage. Extra-long driveway leads to 2 car side entry garage with add’l space for a 3rd car. Recent upgrade of add’l concrete slab, solar screen window coverings, designer lighting, new fans, modern trim fireplace. Quite mature neighborhood near community Pool, Elementary and Middle Schools. Ideal layout with 4 Bedrooms, 2 baths and living spaces on the first floor, with large bonus area upstairs. Bonus room is perfect for a kids retreat or mancave. Kitchen renovation features new flooring, Granite countertops, modern color cabinets, built in TV, Island, new stove & cook top.
